title: Video: REID – Diptera
content:
Having made a name for themselves with videos for the likes of Blackbird Blackbird, Mmoths and Beat Culture, amongst others, Feel Good Lost have released their newest offering in the form of beautifully fitting visuals for REID’s Diptera. Showing REID himself performing the track, set to a background of crashing waves and blustery, idyllic cliffs, cavorting in time with the hypnotic track, it’s safe to say that it’s yet another success for both the musician and Feel Good Lost.

Reid // Diptera from Feel Good Lost on Vimeo.
